[div class=p 
	"The purpose of this page is to document all of the known tricks of the game Bomberman 64 (N64).
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Because of the nature of this site, we concentrate here on tricks that are difficult to play in real time, but are useful in the making of tool-assisted speedruns. For most of the tricks, a 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=frame advance|href=/Glossary)
	" feature in an emulator is a definite must-have.
	$LF
]div
